			<div class="content" id="post-content-3632397">
									

<p>With the approval of <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacob-conwell" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1372582); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1372582&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1510661529" alt="Jacob Conwell" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1372582)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacob-conwell" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1372582); return false;">Jacob Conwell</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/modern-erasmus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3129691); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3129691&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1510661529" alt="Modern_Erasmus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3129691)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/modern-erasmus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3129691); return false;">Modern_Erasmus</a></span>, as well as the wonderfully thorough advice of <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mlister" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3027978); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3027978&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1510661529" alt="mlister" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3027978)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mlister" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3027978); return false;">mlister</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tretter" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1422059); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1422059&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1510661529" alt="tretter" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1422059)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tretter" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1422059); return false;">tretter</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1581620); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1581620&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1510661529" alt="DarkStuff" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1581620)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1581620); return false;">DarkStuff</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/greenwolf" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1814684); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1814684&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1510661529" alt="GreenWolf" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1814684)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/greenwolf" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1814684); return false;">GreenWolf</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/9volt" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2800867); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2800867&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1510661529" alt="9Volt" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2800867)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/9volt" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2800867); return false;">9Volt</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drmagnus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(318209); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=318209&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1510661529" alt="DrMagnus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=318209)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drmagnus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(318209); return false;">DrMagnus</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/metaphysician" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1698079); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1698079&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1510661529" alt="Metaphysician" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1698079)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/metaphysician" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1698079); return false;">Metaphysician</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/theduckman" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(224440); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=224440&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1510661529" alt="TheDuckman" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=224440)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/theduckman" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(224440); return false;">TheDuckman</a></span>, and several others that i may have forgotten<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-337501-1" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-337501-1')">1</a></sup>, the Factory is back in business! I'd like to thank everyone involved; you all wrote this as much as I did.</p>
<p>Of note is that the main page has several GOI formats that explain the nature of the Factory in multiple contradictory ways. This was a conscious decision by myself as the Factory has no real universally agreed upon interpretation, and so each of these formats is representative of a different headcanon that I was able to get summarized for me. As such, no single GOi format is actually the &quot;Correct&quot; interpretation, and none should be treated as such. If you have a headcanon for the Factory that you think should be included here, please PM me with a summary of your headcanon, and I’ll try to add it, provided there are enough GOIs to describe the Factory.</p>
